1
00:02:54,290 --> 00:02:55,335
The tune..

2
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:41,947
You remember the tune?

3
00:04:23,894 --> 00:04:26,050
Hey baby. I'm on the way.

4
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:28,347
Shall we meet directly
at the restaurant?

5
00:04:28,557 --> 00:04:31,503
Sanjana, I am sorry. We'll have
to cancel today's dinner plan.

6
00:04:31,633 --> 00:04:33,597
I have an important meeting
with a client.

7
00:04:33,727 --> 00:04:35,097
I can't miss it.

8
00:04:35,762 --> 00:04:37,389
Baby, it's my birthday.

9
00:04:37,886 --> 00:04:39,800
We can at least
have dinner together.

10
00:04:39,930 --> 00:04:42,345
Sanjana, we can celebrate
your birthday tomorrow.

11
00:04:42,690 --> 00:04:43,721
This meeting is important.

12
00:04:43,851 --> 00:04:45,411
I really need to go.
I'll see you at home.

13
00:04:45,752 --> 00:04:48,074
And yeah.. Happy birthday.

14
00:04:51,493 --> 00:04:53,252
Happy birthday to me.

15
00:05:53,221 --> 00:05:54,587
Happy birthday!

16
00:05:54,717 --> 00:05:57,911
Surprise!
- Anu! Oh my, God!

17
00:05:59,667 --> 00:06:03,190
"Happy birthday to you!"

18
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:06,778
"Happy birthday to you!"

19
00:06:06,908 --> 00:06:10,837
"Happy birthday, dear Sanjana."

20
00:06:10,967 --> 00:06:14,795
"Happy birthday to you!"
- Thank you.

21
00:06:18,281 --> 00:06:20,757
Thank you so much, Anu.
It's so sweet of you.

22
00:06:20,887 --> 00:06:23,593
Don't thank me,
thank your husband.

23
00:06:23,723 --> 00:06:26,014
He's organized all this.

24
00:06:26,263 --> 00:06:27,431
Kabir?

25
00:06:28,143 --> 00:06:31,431
But he's busy with some client..
- He knew he'll be late.

26
00:06:31,695 --> 00:06:33,884
That's why
he organized this party

27
00:06:34,014 --> 00:06:36,347
and called us all here.

28
00:06:37,342 --> 00:06:40,930
Come on. Cut the cake before
your birthday gets over.

29
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:43,560
Cut my birthday cake
without Kabir?

30
00:06:44,554 --> 00:06:45,421
Never.

31
00:06:45,551 --> 00:06:51,222
Sanjana! It's hard to say
who loves whom the most?

32
00:06:51,759 --> 00:06:54,175
You both are mad.
Absolutely crazy.

33
00:06:55,484 --> 00:06:58,950
Honestly, you two
make me really jealous.

34
00:07:00,385 --> 00:07:03,884
By the way, Sanju,
meet my cousin Chitra.

35
00:07:04,014 --> 00:07:05,732
Hi.
- Happy birthday.

36
00:07:05,862 --> 00:07:06,675
Thank you.

37
00:07:06,805 --> 00:07:09,880
I am sorry for coming
here uninvited..

38
00:07:10,133 --> 00:07:10,998
Are you mad?

39
00:07:11,128 --> 00:07:12,648
You're most welcome.
- Thank you.

40
00:07:12,778 --> 00:07:16,514
Sanju, she's an expert
tarot card reader.

41
00:07:16,930 --> 00:07:19,888
If there's anything you want
to know anything about yourself.

42
00:07:20,184 --> 00:07:21,347
Here she is.

43
00:07:21,477 --> 00:07:23,888
She knows everything.

44
00:07:24,018 --> 00:07:27,051
I hope you don't mind.
I don't believe in these things.

45
00:07:27,248 --> 00:07:30,160
Why learn about
yourself from others?

46
00:07:30,423 --> 00:07:32,492
And I've got everything.
And I'm doing good.

47
00:07:32,622 --> 00:07:34,117
Of course you are.

48
00:07:34,247 --> 00:07:36,320
But don't you want to know

49
00:07:36,450 --> 00:07:39,442
whether you'll have
the fortune forever?

50
00:07:48,332 --> 00:07:50,544
You always end up losing

51
00:07:50,674 --> 00:07:54,818
everyone you love
or is close to your heart.

52
00:07:56,272 --> 00:07:58,188
Do you agree?

53
00:08:00,416 --> 00:08:01,790
Right or wrong?

54
00:08:04,596 --> 00:08:06,122
A bit of both.

55
00:08:17,491 --> 00:08:19,296
Have you lost something?

56
00:08:23,934 --> 00:08:25,323
Strange, because

57
00:08:25,965 --> 00:08:27,914
this card indicates that

58
00:08:28,333 --> 00:08:33,706
you're going to find
what you lost.

59
00:08:35,188 --> 00:08:36,877
Maybe someone's coming back.

60
00:09:18,119 --> 00:09:25,473
"The moon's missing
from the sky."

61
00:09:27,063 --> 00:09:34,336
"And descended in my home."

62
00:09:35,978 --> 00:09:41,243
"I am so fortunate"

63
00:09:41,373 --> 00:09:52,166
"like my wish has
been fulfilled."

64
00:09:53,779 --> 00:10:02,543
"My love, I can't live
a moment without you."

65
00:10:02,948 --> 00:10:10,110
"Desire to have you
has made me crazy."

66
00:10:36,531 --> 00:10:39,747
Kabir, I want us
to spend time together.

67
00:10:40,325 --> 00:10:41,997
I've told you
a thousand times before.

68
00:10:42,291 --> 00:10:44,122
I don't want nothing
and no one between us.

69
00:10:44,663 --> 00:10:45,830
Just you and me.

70
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:48,103
But you can't live with me.

71
00:10:48,233 --> 00:10:50,411
There's always some surprise,
or party or people..

72
00:10:50,541 --> 00:10:53,206
And then there's your career,
your meetings, your job.

73
00:10:53,549 --> 00:10:55,830
Sanjana, you wanted
to flee from Kerala, right?

74
00:10:56,191 --> 00:10:57,243
You wanted to come here.

75
00:10:57,373 --> 00:11:00,956
To start a new life.
A better life, better lifestyle.

76
00:11:01,488 --> 00:11:03,789
Isn't that what we
needed to be happy, right?

77
00:11:04,417 --> 00:11:07,909
But for that, one has to work,
stay apart for a while.

78
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:09,756
I don't want to stay apart.

79
00:11:10,666 --> 00:11:12,133
I don't want this.

80
00:11:13,889 --> 00:11:15,289
I just want you.

81
00:11:15,675 --> 00:11:17,709
Your time, your company.

82
00:11:18,747 --> 00:11:20,331
Am I asking for too much?

83
00:11:21,497 --> 00:11:23,867
Fleeing from Kerala didn't
mean that we grow apart too.

84
00:11:23,997 --> 00:11:25,747
What do you want me
to do, Sanjana?

85
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:29,159
Quit my job and stay at home to
assure you nothing has changed.

86
00:11:29,289 --> 00:11:31,297
Everything...
Everything is still the same.

87
00:11:32,694 --> 00:11:34,617
Or let's go to Kerala?
Would you like that?

88
00:11:34,747 --> 00:11:35,659
No.

89
00:11:35,789 --> 00:11:38,243
The root of this problem is
this place. Let's just go back.

90
00:11:38,373 --> 00:11:39,539
No.

91
00:11:42,862 --> 00:11:46,242
Neither that city
nor that house.

92
00:11:48,873 --> 00:11:51,484
That place is littered
with Anjana's memories.

93
00:11:52,609 --> 00:11:54,715
Everywhere.

94
00:11:56,437 --> 00:11:58,317
I won't go back to Kerala.

95
00:12:00,541 --> 00:12:01,385
No.

96
00:12:09,665 --> 00:12:10,716
Hello.

97
00:12:16,996 --> 00:12:18,039
Okay.

98
00:12:19,105 --> 00:12:20,289
What happened?

99
00:12:22,330 --> 00:12:23,921
Mom's in the hospital.

100
00:12:26,517 --> 00:12:28,309
We'll have to go to Kerala.

101
00:12:52,122 --> 00:12:53,103
You okay?

102
00:12:56,063 --> 00:12:56,987
Yes.

103
00:13:02,330 --> 00:13:04,583
I cannot forgive myself.

104
00:13:07,152 --> 00:13:08,956
I am really selfish,
right, Kabir?

105
00:13:09,294 --> 00:13:10,630
Not at all.

106
00:13:11,497 --> 00:13:12,956
Not at all.

107
00:13:16,893 --> 00:13:19,122
If I hadn't insisted
for an operation

108
00:13:19,802 --> 00:13:21,956
then Anjana would've been..
- Sanjana.

109
00:13:22,413 --> 00:13:24,566
It wasn't you,
it was the operation.

110
00:13:25,808 --> 00:13:27,808
No one wants
to be born like that.

111
00:13:29,050 --> 00:13:30,626
No one wants a life like that.

112
00:13:32,389 --> 00:13:34,333
It was an accident. A mishap.

113
00:13:36,099 --> 00:13:37,424
Not selfishness.

114
00:14:24,916 --> 00:14:27,576
Look, she suffered
a serious blow to her head.

115
00:14:27,706 --> 00:14:29,700
She's paralyzed neck down.

116
00:14:29,830 --> 00:14:32,368
She can't speak or walk.

117
00:14:32,498 --> 00:14:34,914
Also, there's a blood clot
in her brain.

118
00:14:35,165 --> 00:14:37,317
We found it in her MRI scan.

119
00:14:38,331 --> 00:14:40,009
We may need to operate her.

120
00:14:42,084 --> 00:14:43,331
Thank you, Doctor.

121
00:14:46,161 --> 00:14:47,473
Sanjana.

122
00:15:12,716 --> 00:15:14,072
Come on, Leo.

123
00:15:17,829 --> 00:15:20,155
Yes, I'll take that.
Thank you. - Okay.

124
00:16:04,071 --> 00:16:06,245
Shall we?
- Yes.

125
00:18:07,159 --> 00:18:08,372
Five!

126
00:18:16,251 --> 00:18:17,835
Anjana.

127
00:18:23,289 --> 00:18:24,665
Sanjana?

128
00:18:30,413 --> 00:18:32,631
Are you Mangala?

129
00:18:32,881 --> 00:18:34,115
Yes, I..

130
00:18:35,330 --> 00:18:36,534
How are you?

131
00:18:36,664 --> 00:18:38,956
I'm okay. And you?

132
00:18:39,178 --> 00:18:41,789
I am fine.

133
00:18:42,166 --> 00:18:44,820
It's all right.
Some ups and downs.

134
00:18:46,039 --> 00:18:47,593
How's madam?

135
00:18:49,788 --> 00:18:51,539
She's being treated.

136
00:18:51,892 --> 00:18:53,456
It's serious.

137
00:18:57,681 --> 00:18:58,763
Who's she?

138
00:18:58,893 --> 00:19:01,446
She's my daughter-in-law, Jaya.
- Hello.

139
00:19:01,576 --> 00:19:03,393
My son's biggest mistake.

140
00:19:04,165 --> 00:19:06,266
They got married
three months ago.

141
00:19:06,623 --> 00:19:10,243
So I brought her here,
to work with me.

142
00:19:10,373 --> 00:19:11,638
I see.

143
00:19:12,616 --> 00:19:16,456
Do you know
what happened that day?

144
00:19:16,767 --> 00:19:18,493
That accident?

145
00:19:18,623 --> 00:19:20,700
I have no clue.

146
00:19:20,830 --> 00:19:23,456
But there was a big storm
that night.

147
00:19:23,771 --> 00:19:26,034
It was such a fierce storm

148
00:19:26,164 --> 00:19:28,700
that the ceiling
of the outhouse collapsed.

149
00:19:28,830 --> 00:19:31,661
Madam was lying outside
the outhouse, unconscious.

150
00:19:33,533 --> 00:19:34,768
Outhouse?

151
00:19:44,825 --> 00:19:46,878
Why do you always
keep it locked?

152
00:19:47,008 --> 00:19:47,992
Why don't you open it?

153
00:19:48,122 --> 00:19:49,747
How can we, sir?

154
00:19:50,235 --> 00:19:52,122
It's been closed
for seven years.

155
00:19:52,422 --> 00:19:54,493
I've been working here
since five years.

156
00:19:55,416 --> 00:19:57,789
I asked madam once, and she said

157
00:19:58,143 --> 00:20:00,773
this was Sanjana
and Anjana's playroom.

158
00:20:01,310 --> 00:20:03,894
After Anjana's death,
Sanjana locked this place.

159
00:20:04,446 --> 00:20:08,076
She said, this place is
filled with Anjana's memories.

160
00:20:08,268 --> 00:20:10,456
Her toys, and..

161
00:20:12,248 --> 00:20:14,451
And Anjana too.
- Mother!

162
00:20:14,581 --> 00:20:16,380
What nonsense! Anjana too!

163
00:20:16,886 --> 00:20:18,242
Please open it.

164
00:20:18,372 --> 00:20:20,997
Sir..
- Get the key, please.

165
00:20:21,588 --> 00:20:23,297
Thank you.
- Let's go.

166
00:24:46,872 --> 00:24:48,237
Who is it?

167
00:25:06,488 --> 00:25:08,982
Kabir!
Oh, God! You scared me.

168
00:25:09,112 --> 00:25:09,969
And you amaze me.

169
00:25:10,099 --> 00:25:11,827
What are you doing here
at 2 o'clock in the night?

170
00:25:11,957 --> 00:25:14,256
Kabir, I.. I heard some noises.

171
00:25:15,339 --> 00:25:17,209
What noise? Are you crazy?

172
00:25:17,339 --> 00:25:18,278
Really, Kabir.

173
00:25:18,408 --> 00:25:20,277
I heard some noises
and came to inspect.. - Sanjana.

174
00:25:20,407 --> 00:25:23,103
If there were any sounds,
I'd have heard them too, right?

175
00:25:23,434 --> 00:25:25,414
You didn't hear anything?
- No.

176
00:25:25,802 --> 00:25:27,369
Come on.
- Kabir, trust me.

177
00:25:27,499 --> 00:25:28,569
I heard some noises.

178
00:25:28,699 --> 00:25:29,870
It must be coming
from some other house.

179
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,736
Come on. Let's go back
to sleep, come on.

180
00:25:38,521 --> 00:25:39,451
Mr. Kabir.
- Yeah.

181
00:25:39,581 --> 00:25:40,807
There have been
some complications.

182
00:25:40,937 --> 00:25:42,451
We need to operate
on her immediately.

183
00:25:42,581 --> 00:25:44,152
I think you should get her
as quick as you can.

184
00:25:44,282 --> 00:25:45,101
What?

185
00:25:45,870 --> 00:25:47,535
'Paging for Sister Parvati.'

186
00:25:47,665 --> 00:25:50,034
'Sister Parvati please report
to ward 5.'

187
00:25:50,164 --> 00:25:53,824
'Sister Parvati please
report to ward 5.'

188
00:25:59,294 --> 00:26:00,575
Yes, Mohit, go ahead.

189
00:26:02,469 --> 00:26:03,373
What?

190
00:26:04,072 --> 00:26:06,028
No, Mohit,
you can't take a leave.

191
00:26:06,158 --> 00:26:07,164
Kabir!

192
00:26:09,456 --> 00:26:10,564
Sorry.

193
00:26:11,326 --> 00:26:12,367
Buddy..

194
00:26:12,497 --> 00:26:13,686
Mohit, firstly I am
not in the office.

195
00:26:13,816 --> 00:26:14,659
And now you want a leave too.

196
00:26:14,789 --> 00:26:15,742
Those are very
important clients.

197
00:26:15,872 --> 00:26:17,623
Somebody has to be
there to handle them.

198
00:26:18,015 --> 00:26:19,860
Who will do it?

199
00:26:21,830 --> 00:26:24,039
I don't know. I am stuck
in this goddamn place.

200
00:26:24,535 --> 00:26:26,076
Why did all the mothers have to
fall ill at the same time?

201
00:26:26,206 --> 00:26:27,503
I just don't understand..

202
00:26:30,755 --> 00:26:32,039
I'll call you back.

203
00:26:35,296 --> 00:26:37,626
Sanjana, I am sorry.
I didn't mean that.

204
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:54,164
Sanjana.

205
00:26:55,078 --> 00:26:55,956
I am sorry.

206
00:26:56,554 --> 00:26:57,700
Actually, I am quite
stressed because of the work..

207
00:26:57,830 --> 00:26:59,331
Just go, Kabir.

208
00:27:00,043 --> 00:27:01,539
Don't worry about me.

209
00:27:01,979 --> 00:27:03,984
I'll handle everything
here, alone.

210
00:27:04,873 --> 00:27:06,789
And anyway,
what will you do here?

211
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:08,711
Just go.

212
00:27:09,882 --> 00:27:11,826
I wanted your support,
not your favor.

213
00:27:11,956 --> 00:27:13,784
Come on, Sanjana. You're making
a big deal out of this.

214
00:27:13,914 --> 00:27:15,004
I am not going anywhere.

215
00:27:15,134 --> 00:27:16,835
And I won't go until
mom doesn't recover.

216
00:27:16,965 --> 00:27:18,456
But I will stay distracted..

217
00:27:18,861 --> 00:27:20,122
I can't help that.

218
00:27:20,947 --> 00:27:22,122
I know that.

219
00:27:23,111 --> 00:27:26,372
I am used to dealing
with my problems alone.

220
00:27:26,502 --> 00:27:28,076
To keep my emotions to myself.

221
00:27:28,206 --> 00:27:30,201
For God's sake Sanjana,
all I said was..

222
00:27:30,331 --> 00:27:31,414
Excuse me.

223
00:27:34,728 --> 00:27:35,876
The operation was successful.

224
00:27:36,006 --> 00:27:37,854
But you can't meet
your mom right now.

225
00:27:38,330 --> 00:27:39,416
In the meantime,
you can complete

226
00:27:39,546 --> 00:27:41,031
some hospital formalities.

227
00:27:41,161 --> 00:27:42,284
Please. Thank you.
- Okay.

228
00:27:42,414 --> 00:27:43,623
Thank you.

229
00:27:48,980 --> 00:27:50,122
I'll take care of it.

230
00:27:50,252 --> 00:27:53,141
It's all right. I'll do it.

231
00:27:53,712 --> 00:27:55,903
Sanjana,
I said I'll take care of it.

232
00:28:06,655 --> 00:28:07,711
Kabir!

233
00:28:09,578 --> 00:28:11,129
Namit sir? You?

234
00:28:11,259 --> 00:28:13,289
It's..
I can't believe it.

235
00:28:13,581 --> 00:28:15,659
How are you?
- Good, sir. Good.

236
00:28:15,789 --> 00:28:17,992
But you tell me this.
You just disappeared for years.

237
00:28:18,122 --> 00:28:19,784
No contact or anything.
What are you doing here?

238
00:28:19,914 --> 00:28:21,516
I mean what are you doing here?
- Hey!

239
00:28:21,646 --> 00:28:22,506
Catch your breath first.

240
00:28:22,636 --> 00:28:25,914
Well.. After seeing you,
I feel perfectly all right.

241
00:28:26,122 --> 00:28:28,951
You haven't changed at all.
Still the same.

242
00:28:29,081 --> 00:28:31,414
Looks and wits.

243
00:28:31,895 --> 00:28:34,919
What are you doing here
at this hour?

244
00:28:35,496 --> 00:28:38,742
Well, sir, my mother-in-law's
admitted in this hospital.

245
00:28:38,872 --> 00:28:41,498
You don't worry,
she is in safe hands.

246
00:28:41,705 --> 00:28:43,289
This is a very good hospital.

247
00:28:43,623 --> 00:28:45,248
And then I am there.

248
00:28:45,499 --> 00:28:47,909
Let me know if I can
be of some help. I'll do it.

249
00:28:48,039 --> 00:28:49,029
Thank you so much, sir.
I know.

250
00:28:49,159 --> 00:28:51,409
But first tell me
what are you doing here?

251
00:28:51,539 --> 00:28:53,789
I am a psychologist
in this hospital.

252
00:28:54,217 --> 00:28:58,456
And I also run a Healing
Institute in Kottayam.

253
00:28:59,250 --> 00:29:00,500
Healing Institute?
- Yeah!

254
00:29:00,630 --> 00:29:01,944
These days I do everything.

255
00:29:02,074 --> 00:29:03,800
Spiritual healing, etcetera.

256
00:29:04,405 --> 00:29:06,706
I have students, I also teach.

257
00:29:06,956 --> 00:29:09,076
Keep my card.
- Thank you, sir.

258
00:29:09,206 --> 00:29:10,284
I.. I will call you, sir.

259
00:29:10,414 --> 00:29:11,451
Sure?
- We'll definitely meet.

260
00:29:11,581 --> 00:29:13,581
Yeah! Okay.
You take care.

261
00:29:14,915 --> 00:29:15,997
Okay?

262
