in this house.

798
01:29:06,897 --> 01:29:08,701
And everything will
be fine after that.

799
01:29:11,856 --> 01:29:12,666
Okay.

800
01:31:44,741 --> 01:31:45,976
Sanjana.

801
01:32:07,512 --> 01:32:10,936
Just like there are
two kinds of human beings.

802
01:32:12,150 --> 01:32:15,205
Similarly,
there are two kinds of spirits.

803
01:32:15,876 --> 01:32:17,541
Good and bad.

804
01:32:18,826 --> 01:32:22,311
Bad spirits often
possess weak bodies.

805
01:32:22,752 --> 01:32:24,306
Trouble them.

806
01:32:24,609 --> 01:32:26,718
