812
01:32:57,773 --> 01:33:00,064
We have very little time.

813
01:33:10,816 --> 01:33:12,592
Hail the Bhoot Puran
(Book of evil)!

814
01:33:13,058 --> 01:33:14,686
Lord have mercy on us.

815
01:33:17,790 --> 01:33:21,534
This Bhoot Puran was
been written by ascetics

816
01:33:21,664 --> 01:33:23,773
thousands of years ago.

817
01:33:24,098 --> 01:33:28,867
We can use the chants written
in them to control the spirit.

818
01:33:29,458 --> 01:33:32,113
Destroy all the
belongings of her sister.

819
01:33:32,243 --> 01:33:34,583
Cover every glass in this house.

820
01:33:34,752 --> 01:33:37,668
Mirrors, photographs,
everything.

821
01:33:37,890 --> 01:33:40,585
Because, as soon as
I start chanting

822
01:33:40,793 --> 01:33:42,816
the spirit will leave her body

823
01:33:43,086 --> 01:33:45,840
and try to hide in these things.

824
01:33:46,032 --> 01:33:48,001
And this shouldn't happen.

825
01:33:48,210 --> 01:33:51,418
I've covered all the
corners of this house

826
01:33:51,720 --> 01:33:54,615
so that the spirit
doesn't leave.

827
01:33:55,459 --> 01:33:58,100
The spirit has to be
destroyed right here.

828
01:33:59,793 --> 01:34:04,629
Once I start chanting,
it will lie, try to distract us.

829
01:34:04,999 --> 01:34:07,168
