873
01:40:33,751 --> 01:40:35,041
What do you mean?

874
01:40:35,818 --> 01:40:37,072
What's all this?

875
01:40:42,779 --> 01:40:45,027
All I got was lies, so I thought

876
01:40:45,157 --> 01:40:49,293
I must lie to know the truth.

877
01:40:50,043 --> 01:40:51,353
Stop talking in riddles.

878
01:40:52,032 --> 01:40:53,335
Be clear.

879
