of death for the other sister.

940
01:45:27,035 --> 01:45:28,544
Remember this.

941
01:45:30,281 --> 01:45:32,697
Anjana loved you very much.

942
01:45:34,333 --> 01:45:36,484
And I love you.

943
01:45:38,494 --> 01:45:40,167
So sorry, Sanjana.

944
01:45:57,795 --> 01:46:00,106
This means Anjana's spirit
is here to take revenge

945
01:46:00,236 --> 01:46:02,942
and, she won't leave
without doing so.

946
01:46:04,767 --> 01:46:09,250
There's something Anjana's
spirit is tethered to.

947
01:46:11,388 --> 01:46:14,526
Before she attacks Sanjana again

948
01:46:15,811 --> 01:46:18,568
you'll have to find
that thing and burn it.

949
01:46:18,904 --> 01:46:19,984
What happened?

950
01:46:20,382 --> 01:46:22,401
Sanjana, he says
something in the house..

951
