01:57:34,782 --> 01:57:36,155
Kabir!

983
01:57:37,946 --> 01:57:39,364
Kabir!

984
01:57:55,156 --> 01:57:56,026
Kabir!

985
01:57:56,156 --> 01:57:56,992
Kabir!

986
