998
01:59:38,991 --> 01:59:41,946
Please, tell me the truth now.

999
01:59:42,249 --> 01:59:43,739
Tell me the truth.

1000
01:59:44,004 --> 01:59:46,077
Kabir..
- Tell me the truth.

1001
01:59:47,094 --> 01:59:49,030
Tell me the truth.

1002
01:59:54,096 --> 01:59:58,761
No? Then I'll make sure
that he only loves me.

1003
02:00:37,873 --> 02:00:42,033
Mom, please.
From now, I am Sanjana.

1004
02:00:42,581 --> 02:00:44,506
I could not help it, Kabir.

1005
02:00:45,005 --> 02:00:47,169
I loved you like crazy.

1006
02:00:47,890 --> 02:00:49,323
I wanted you.

1007
02:00:50,036 --> 02:00:51,484
