1024
02:01:36,633 --> 02:01:38,815
Kabir. Kabir..

1025
02:01:39,922 --> 02:01:43,572
That moment, that day,
that year.

1026
02:01:44,230 --> 02:01:46,231
All the time that
we spent together.

1027
02:01:46,361 --> 02:01:48,137
