1051
02:02:50,914 --> 02:02:52,389
Kabir!

1052
02:02:58,372 --> 02:02:59,431
Kabir!

1053
02:02:59,561 --> 02:03:02,262
You can't leave.
You can't leave.

1054
02:03:02,508 --> 02:03:05,347
I won't let you go.
I won't let you go.

1055
02:03:05,638 --> 02:03:08,139
Say you love me.
Say you love me.

1056
02:03:08,583 --> 02:03:09,602
Say you love me!

